    dc:title "Pentastira eminei sp. nov. (Hemiptera, Fulgoromorpha, Cixiidae) from Türkiye and notes on other Pentastira spp. in Türkiye and the Middle East" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7120038>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7120044> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7120038>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Various portions the male genitalia of Middle Eastern Pentastira spp. a) dorsal habitus of P. bahtiarica anal tube; b) posterior view of P. bahtiarica anal tube; c) posterior view of P. shul anal tube; d) posterior view of P. torossica anal tube; e) internal view of P. superspicata styli; f) posterior view of P. rorida styli; g) ventral habitus of P. superspicata aedeagus; h) dorsal habitus of P. torossica aedeagus; i) ventral habitus of P. bahtiarica aedeagus; j) position of the tooth on the left side of the theca base in P. major; k) position of the tooth on the left side of the theca base in P. megista; l) positioning of the lateral apophyseal ends in P. interjecta laterally; and m) positioning of the lateral apophyseal ends in P. rorida laterally (adapted from Dlabola 1957, 1981, 1985; Linnavuori 1957; Logvinenko 1976; Holzinger et al. 2003)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7120038/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7120044>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Pentastira eminei sp. nov. male genitalia parts. a) dorsal view of anal tube; b) lateral view of anal tube; c) ventral (external) view of styli; d) internal view of styli; e) left lateral view of aedeagus; and f) dorsal view of aedeagus; g) ventral view of aedeagus. Scale bar, 250 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7120044/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

